            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b83844134a1ef271-f09fcd twpub-b83844134a1ef271-6b4cd0\"><p>1.F.4.  Except for the limited right of replacement or refund set forth\nin paragraph 1.F.3, this work is provided to you 'AS-IS' WITH NO OTHER\nWARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO\nWARRANTIES OF MERCHANTIBILITY OR FITNESS FOR ANY PURPOSE.</p></div>"
